text: Yuki Niizawa (born 13 February 1997) is a Japanese female water polo player who participated at the 2017 Summer Universiade, 2018 Asian Games, 2017 World Aquatic Championships, and 2019 World Aquatic Championships. == References == == Other websites == * yuki-niizawa-of-japan getty * yuki-niizawa-jpn-water- polo alamy Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Japanese water polo players
